												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Wry and rueful, remembering it with fond amusement - Nine-Fingers was abducted as a child and, even after being ransomed, left her family to fend for herself. She doesn't speak of her traumatic past with any great pathos - she's seen worse in the city. "
