																	"handle": "h85233c5dgafb9g481fg88d0gf7c6bc5a9e32",
																	"value": "Aye, I remember the spot - by a garden on the Wide. A soft thicket near the market, with ample pockets to pick. Celestia itself, to a street rat looking for shelter. ",
